sentences: Leopoldine took piano lessons from her mother and made her debut as a pianist in 1818.
In 1821 Blahetka began touring Europe, accompanied by her mother, and continued to tour for about twenty years.
In about 1830 the family moved to Boulogne-sur-Mer, France, seeking a better climate.
